nodes.text: A Human female underdweller was working for the IT-3 Interrogator droid "It" in 8 ABY. When "It" and several other underdwellers brought a stolen datapad and the young Wookiee Lumpawarrump to the secret Imperial detention center where the female was stationed, she was ultimately knocked unconscious by Lumpawarrump's father, Chewbacca.
